data.description: Great family home in a great location near the elementary school and park.  Large kitchen with stainless steel appliances, lots of cabinets and counter-space.  The spacious kitchen and dining room are open to the living room which features a fireplace and vaulted ceilings.  The primary suite features a bay window, large, walk-in closet and separate tub and shower.  Both secondary bedrooms have walk-in closets and the generous back yard has the privacy of no back neighbors.  An over-sized garage with built-in work bench.
